<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，凯蒂向山坡跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸和乔伊已经开始做树屋的楼梯了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，爸爸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂边喊，边爬上了卡车的后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她往旧桶里看，拿出了滑轮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然是滑轮啊！”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是做什么的？”凯蒂问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一会儿你就知道。”乔伊回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以用这个杆子挂我的风向袋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是风向袋？”乔伊问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一会儿你就知道。”凯蒂回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁板屋顶在草地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸打开一罐深蓝色的油漆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这儿有一把刷子。”他对乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也想帮忙吗，凯蒂？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。”凯蒂说完，从卡车上跳了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈和我正在做一些事情。再见。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊拿刷子蘸了点油漆，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仔细地刷了第一块铁板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个屋顶一定要看起来很完美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊边说，边转过身去蘸油漆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她转过身来时，麦古正坐在刚刷完漆的铁板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦古！”她说，“油漆还没干呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦古站起来，舔了舔乔伊的脸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>高兴地摇着蓝尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走开。”乔伊喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会把油漆弄洒的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦古跳回去，又坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好狗狗。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦古看着乔伊刷油漆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它的眼睛盯着刷子来回移动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，它伸出爪子，碰了一下刷子 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别动！”乔伊叫道，“你想成为一只蓝色麦古吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狗狗收回蓝色的爪子，抱歉地看着乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了中午，楼梯完成了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁板刷好了，爸爸正在盖墙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊和麦古躺在草地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们俩都粘满了油漆：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的衬衫、它的爪子、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的膝盖、它的尾巴、</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的下巴、它的耳朵，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但乔伊不在乎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为树屋很快就要完工了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天下午，爸爸安上了门和窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他钉上了屋顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“完工了！”乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂、妈妈和爷爷从房子里跑出来看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈带来了一个装满雏菊的花盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把它放进桶里，妈妈！”乔伊从树屋里喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桶放在地上，把手上绑着一根绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>绳子系在滑轮上，滑轮固定在屋顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈把花放在桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在看这个。”乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拉起绳子，滑轮转动，水桶升起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把雏菊从桶里拿了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上来吧，妈妈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家一个接一个地从树屋向外看多诺万家的土地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家打开、关上树屋的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们开了开窗户，试了试滑轮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们为爸爸和乔伊欢呼吧！”凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈、爷爷和凯蒂拍手欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸鞠了一个躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有一件事。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸把新的风向袋安在树屋屋顶上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看！它被挂在杆子上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都抬头看了看风向袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是妈妈帮我做的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“风向袋告诉我们风的强度和方向。”凯蒂解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当风静止时，风向袋也是静止的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像现在一样。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，当风很大的时候，风向袋就会笔直地飞起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂停下来，睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果风是从西南吹来的，注意！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可能是龙卷风来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太酷了，凯蒂。”乔伊说，“谢谢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>